# DSA 210 Project

## Cryptocurrency Analysis (April 14 Milestone)

This project analyzes Bitcoin price movements using BTC OHLCV data and USDT market cap data.

## Data
- BTC hourly dataset (processed from archive)
- USDT market cap data (CSV)

## Steps
- Data cleaning
- Merging datasets
- Feature engineering
- Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
- Hypothesis testing

## Outputs
- final_dataset.csv
- analysis notebook

## AI Usage
AI was used for technical assistance in converting the BTC archive dataset into a usable format and for debugging code. All analysis decisions were made by the student.
